(154, 1, '2018-05-13 16:45:40', '2018-05-13 16:45:40', '<div class=\"product-fullinfo__item\">\r\n<div class=\"product-fullinfo__inner\">\r\n<div class=\"typo\">\r\n\r\nThe phone was taken for replacement of iPhone 6, which satisfied me on a number of characteristics (primarily the inability to record the conversation). I must say that the phone is not used as the player (can’t assess the sound quality) and for games (can’t say anything about performance). Was very surprised that for such money it is possible to have a completely bug-free (!) Chinese camera: more than a month of work has never crashed, not flew any applications, etc. I especially appreciate the fact that the camera works very quickly. I often have to take photos of documents on your phone and this device perfectly copes with it. Sorry marketers did not want to tie NFC((( In General took, and now purchase it for all employees of the office as a workhorse.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"product-fullinfo__item\">\r\n<div class=\"product-fullinfo__header\"></div>\r\n</div>', '64GB Xiaomi Mi A1 Golden', '<div class=\"short-description typo typo--small\">\r\n\r\nThe phone was taken for replacement of iPhone 6, which satisfied me on a number of characteristics (primarily the inability to record the conversation).\r\n\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '64gb-xiaomi-mi-a1', '', '', '2018-05-13 17:02:32', '2018-05-13 17:02:32', '', 0, 'http://rewooc/?post_type=product&#038;p=154', 0, 'product', '', 0),
